{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 81,
  "title": "第八十一章（不積）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "信言不美。"
    },
    {
      "text": "美言不信。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知者不博。"
    },
    {
      "text": "博者不知。"
    },
    {
      "text": "善者不多。"
    },
    {
      "text": "多者不善。"
    },
    {
      "text": "聖人无積。"
    },
    {
      "text": "既以為人，己愈有。"
    },
    {
      "text": "既以予人，己愈多。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故："
    },
    {
      "text": "天之道，利而不害。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之道，為而弗爭。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "美言者，滋美之華辭。不信者，飾偽多空虛也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善者，以道修身也。不綵文也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "辯者，謂巧言也。不善者，舌致患也。山有玉，掘其山；水有珠，濁其淵；辯口多言，亡其身。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "知者，謂知道之士。不博者，守一元也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 18,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "博者，多見聞也。不知者，失要真也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人積德不積財，有德以教愚，有財以與貧也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "既以為人施設德化，己愈有德。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "既以財賄布施與人，而財益多，如日月之光，無有盡時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 3,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天生萬物，愛育之，令長大，無所傷害也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人法天所施為，化成事就，不與下爭功名，故能全其聖功也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "本在樸也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "極在一也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無私自有，唯善是與，任物而已。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "物所尊也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "物所歸也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 3,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "動常生成之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "順天之利不相傷也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
